title: Rifftrax Indiana Jones & The Kingdom of the Crystal Skull
description:
I noticed no one had put this up so here it is, Indiana Jones and The Kingdom of the Crystal Skull with the Rifftrax track included.
This AVI has both the original soundtrack and the rifftrax soundtrack, so make sure you use a player that can switch soundtracks, VLC Media is a good one.
I&#039;m pretty sure that I have the Rifftrax synced throughout the whole movie, sorry if it&#039;s off a little bit at any part.
Also, please go to www.rifftrax.com and donate so that we will keep getting these rifftraxs.
Thanks a lot everyone and enjoy!
